# Root-level compiled scratch outputs. `hew build` at the repo root drops a
# bare executable plus its `.o`/`.ll` next to it; these are never source and
# must not land in history. Root-anchored so legitimate `.o`/`.ll` elsewhere
# (and any tracked executable) are unaffected.
/*.o
/*.ll
/dist_node
/let_else_tuple_payload
/owned_nested_tuple_record
/sort_prog
/stdlib_io_scanner_file_oracle
/wire_json_vec_option_roundtrip

